<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="show-off">show off</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[非正式用语] 卖弄；炫耀：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Although some people like to show off their wealth, income is a very private matter for most Americans.
虽然有些人喜欢炫耀自己的财富，但对大多数美国人而言，收入是一件非常隐私的事情。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 1</footer></div></div>